{"surah":{"number":78,"name":"النبإ","englishName":"An-Naba","englishTranslation":"The Tidings","ayahCount":40},"sources":["Quran.com API v4 (word-by-word Uthmani + English glosses + word audio)","AlQuran.cloud / Tanzil quran-uthmani (independent text verification)","AlQuran.cloud / Saheeh International (flowing English translation)","Quranic Arabic Corpus morphology (word roots)"],"generatedAt":"2026-07-03T04:01:37.886Z","ayahs":[{"number":1,"translation":"About what are they asking one another?","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"عَمَّ","english":"About what","translit":"ʿamma","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"يَتَسَآءَلُونَ","english":"are they asking one another","translit":"yatasāalūna","root":"سأل"}]},{"number":2,"translation":"About the great news -","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"عَنِ","english":"About","translit":"ʿani","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلنَّبَإِ","english":"the News","translit":"l-naba-i","root":"نبأ"},{"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلْعَظِيمِ","english":"the Great","translit":"l-ʿaẓīmi","root":"عظم"}]},{"number":3,"translation":"That over which they are in disagreement.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِى","english":"(About) which","translit":"alladhī","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"هُمْ","english":"they","translit":"hum","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"فِيهِ","english":"(are) concerning it","translit":"fīhi","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"مُخْتَلِفُونَ","english":"(in) disagreement","translit":"mukh'talifūna","root":"خلف"}]},{"number":4,"translation":"No! They are going to know.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"كَلَّا","english":"Nay","translit":"kallā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"سَيَعْلَمُونَ","english":"(soon) they will know","translit":"sayaʿlamūna","root":"علم"}]},{"number":5,"translation":"Then, no! They are going to know.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"ثُمَّ","english":"Then","translit":"thumma","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"كَلَّا","english":"Nay","translit":"kallā","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"سَيَعْلَمُونَ","english":"(soon) they will know","translit":"sayaʿlamūna","root":"علم"}]},{"number":6,"translation":"Have We not made the earth a resting place?","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"أَلَمْ","english":"Have not","translit":"alam","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"نَجْعَلِ","english":"We made","translit":"najʿali","root":"جعل"},{"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلْأَرْضَ","english":"the earth","translit":"l-arḍa","root":"أرض"},{"position":4,"arabic":"مِهَـٰدًۭا","english":"a resting place","translit":"mihādan","root":"مهد"}]},{"number":7,"translation":"And the mountains as stakes?","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَٱلْجِبَالَ","english":"And the mountains","translit":"wal-jibāla","root":"جبل"},{"position":2,"arabic":"أَوْتَادًۭا","english":"(as) pegs","translit":"awtādan","root":"وتد"}]},{"number":8,"translation":"And We created you in pairs","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَخَلَقْنَـٰكُمْ","english":"And We created you","translit":"wakhalaqnākum","root":"خلق"},{"position":2,"arabic":"أَزْوَٰجًۭا","english":"(in) pairs","translit":"azwājan","root":"زوج"}]},{"number":9,"translation":"And made your sleep [a means for] rest","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَجَعَلْنَا","english":"And We made","translit":"wajaʿalnā","root":"جعل"},{"position":2,"arabic":"نَوْمَكُمْ","english":"your sleep","translit":"nawmakum","root":"نوم"},{"position":3,"arabic":"سُبَاتًۭا","english":"(for) rest","translit":"subātan","root":"سبت"}]},{"number":10,"translation":"And made the night as clothing","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَجَعَلْنَا","english":"And We made","translit":"wajaʿalnā","root":"جعل"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلَّيْلَ","english":"the night","translit":"al-layla","root":"ليل"},{"position":3,"arabic":"لِبَاسًۭا","english":"(as) covering","translit":"libāsan","root":"لبس"}]},{"number":11,"translation":"And made the day for livelihood","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَجَعَلْنَا","english":"And We made","translit":"wajaʿalnā","root":"جعل"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلنَّهَارَ","english":"the day","translit":"l-nahāra","root":"نهر"},{"position":3,"arabic":"مَعَاشًۭا","english":"(for) livelihood","translit":"maʿāshan","root":"عيش"}]},{"number":12,"translation":"And constructed above you seven strong [heavens]","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَبَنَيْنَا","english":"And We constructed","translit":"wabanaynā","root":"بني"},{"position":2,"arabic":"فَوْقَكُمْ","english":"over you","translit":"fawqakum","root":"فوق"},{"position":3,"arabic":"سَبْعًۭا","english":"seven","translit":"sabʿan","root":"سبع"},{"position":4,"arabic":"شِدَادًۭا","english":"strong","translit":"shidādan","root":"شدد"}]},{"number":13,"translation":"And made [therein] a burning lamp","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَجَعَلْنَا","english":"And We placed","translit":"wajaʿalnā","root":"جعل"},{"position":2,"arabic":"سِرَاجًۭا","english":"a lamp","translit":"sirājan","root":"سرج"},{"position":3,"arabic":"وَهَّاجًۭا","english":"burning","translit":"wahhājan","root":"وهج"}]},{"number":14,"translation":"And sent down, from the rain clouds, pouring water","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَأَنزَلْنَا","english":"And We sent down","translit":"wa-anzalnā","root":"نزل"},{"position":2,"arabic":"مِنَ","english":"from","translit":"mina","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلْمُعْصِرَٰتِ","english":"the rain clouds","translit":"l-muʿ'ṣirāti","root":"عصر"},{"position":4,"arabic":"مَآءًۭ","english":"water","translit":"māan","root":"موه"},{"position":5,"arabic":"ثَجَّاجًۭا","english":"pouring abundantly","translit":"thajjājan","root":"ثجج"}]},{"number":15,"translation":"That We may bring forth thereby grain and vegetation","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"لِّنُخْرِجَ","english":"That We may bring forth","translit":"linukh'rija","root":"خرج"},{"position":2,"arabic":"بِهِۦ","english":"thereby","translit":"bihi","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"حَبًّۭا","english":"grain","translit":"ḥabban","root":"حبب"},{"position":4,"arabic":"وَنَبَاتًۭا","english":"and vegetation","translit":"wanabātan","root":"نبت"}]},{"number":16,"translation":"And gardens of entwined growth.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَجَنَّـٰتٍ","english":"And gardens","translit":"wajannātin","root":"جنن"},{"position":2,"arabic":"أَلْفَافًا","english":"(of) thick foliage","translit":"alfāfan","root":"لفف"}]},{"number":17,"translation":"Indeed, the Day of Judgement is an appointed time -","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"إِنَّ","english":"Indeed","translit":"inna","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"يَوْمَ","english":"(the) Day","translit":"yawma","root":"يوم"},{"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلْفَصْلِ","english":"(of) the Judgment","translit":"l-faṣli","root":"فصل"},{"position":4,"arabic":"كَانَ","english":"is","translit":"kāna","root":"كون"},{"position":5,"arabic":"مِيقَـٰتًۭا","english":"an appointed time","translit":"mīqātan","root":"وقت"}]},{"number":18,"translation":"The Day the Horn is blown and you will come forth in multitudes","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"يَوْمَ","english":"(The) Day","translit":"yawma","root":"يوم"},{"position":2,"arabic":"يُنفَخُ","english":"(in which) shall be blown","translit":"yunfakhu","root":"نفخ"},{"position":3,"arabic":"فِى","english":"in","translit":"fī","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلصُّورِ","english":"the trumpet","translit":"l-ṣūri","root":"صور"},{"position":5,"arabic":"فَتَأْتُونَ","english":"and you will come forth","translit":"fatatūna","root":"أتي"},{"position":6,"arabic":"أَفْوَاجًۭا","english":"(in) crowds","translit":"afwājan","root":"فوج"}]},{"number":19,"translation":"And the heaven is opened and will become gateways","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَفُتِحَتِ","english":"And is opened","translit":"wafutiḥati","root":"فتح"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلسَّمَآءُ","english":"the heaven","translit":"l-samāu","root":"سمو"},{"position":3,"arabic":"فَكَانَتْ","english":"and becomes","translit":"fakānat","root":"كون"},{"position":4,"arabic":"أَبْوَٰبًۭا","english":"gateways","translit":"abwāban","root":"بوب"}]},{"number":20,"translation":"And the mountains are removed and will be [but] a mirage.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَسُيِّرَتِ","english":"And are moved","translit":"wasuyyirati","root":"سير"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلْجِبَالُ","english":"the mountains","translit":"l-jibālu","root":"جبل"},{"position":3,"arabic":"فَكَانَتْ","english":"and become","translit":"fakānat","root":"كون"},{"position":4,"arabic":"سَرَابًا","english":"a mirage","translit":"sarāban","root":"سرب"}]},{"number":21,"translation":"Indeed, Hell has been lying in wait","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"إِنَّ","english":"Indeed","translit":"inna","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"جَهَنَّمَ","english":"Hell","translit":"jahannama","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"كَانَتْ","english":"is","translit":"kānat","root":"كون"},{"position":4,"arabic":"مِرْصَادًۭا","english":"lying in wait","translit":"mir'ṣādan","root":"رصد"}]},{"number":22,"translation":"For the transgressors, a place of return,","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"لِّلطَّـٰغِينَ","english":"For the transgressors","translit":"lilṭṭāghīna","root":"طغي"},{"position":2,"arabic":"مَـَٔابًۭا","english":"a place of return","translit":"maāban","root":"أوب"}]},{"number":23,"translation":"In which they will remain for ages [unending].","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"لَّـٰبِثِينَ","english":"(They will) be remaining","translit":"lābithīna","root":"لبث"},{"position":2,"arabic":"فِيهَآ","english":"therein","translit":"fīhā","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"أَحْقَابًۭا","english":"(for) ages","translit":"aḥqāban","root":"حقب"}]},{"number":24,"translation":"They will not taste therein [any] coolness or drink","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"لَّا","english":"Not","translit":"lā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"يَذُوقُونَ","english":"they will taste","translit":"yadhūqūna","root":"ذوق"},{"position":3,"arabic":"فِيهَا","english":"therein","translit":"fīhā","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"بَرْدًۭا","english":"coolness","translit":"bardan","root":"برد"},{"position":5,"arabic":"وَلَا","english":"and not","translit":"walā","root":""},{"position":6,"arabic":"شَرَابًا","english":"any drink","translit":"sharāban","root":"شرب"}]},{"number":25,"translation":"Except scalding water and [foul] purulence -","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"إِلَّا","english":"Except","translit":"illā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"حَمِيمًۭا","english":"scalding water","translit":"ḥamīman","root":"حمم"},{"position":3,"arabic":"وَغَسَّاقًۭا","english":"and purulence","translit":"waghassāqan","root":"غسق"}]},{"number":26,"translation":"An appropriate recompense.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"جَزَآءًۭ","english":"A recompense","translit":"jazāan","root":"جزي"},{"position":2,"arabic":"وِفَاقًا","english":"appropriate","translit":"wifāqan","root":"وفق"}]},{"number":27,"translation":"Indeed, they were not expecting an account","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"إِنَّهُمْ","english":"Indeed, they","translit":"innahum","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"كَانُوا۟","english":"were","translit":"kānū","root":"كون"},{"position":3,"arabic":"لَا","english":"not","translit":"lā","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"يَرْجُونَ","english":"expecting","translit":"yarjūna","root":"رجو"},{"position":5,"arabic":"حِسَابًۭا","english":"an account","translit":"ḥisāban","root":"حسب"}]},{"number":28,"translation":"And denied Our verses with [emphatic] denial.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَكَذَّبُوا۟","english":"And they denied","translit":"wakadhabū","root":"كذب"},{"position":2,"arabic":"بِـَٔايَـٰتِنَا","english":"Our Signs","translit":"biāyātinā","root":"أيي"},{"position":3,"arabic":"كِذَّابًۭا","english":"(with) denial","translit":"kidhāban","root":"كذب"}]},{"number":29,"translation":"But all things We have enumerated in writing.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَكُلَّ","english":"And every","translit":"wakulla","root":"كلل"},{"position":2,"arabic":"شَىْءٍ","english":"thing","translit":"shayin","root":"شيأ"},{"position":3,"arabic":"أَحْصَيْنَـٰهُ","english":"We have enumerated it","translit":"aḥṣaynāhu","root":"حصي"},{"position":4,"arabic":"كِتَـٰبًۭا","english":"(in) a Book","translit":"kitāban","root":"كتب"}]},{"number":30,"translation":"\"So taste [the penalty], and never will We increase you except in torment.\"","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَذُوقُوا۟","english":"So taste","translit":"fadhūqū","root":"ذوق"},{"position":2,"arabic":"فَلَن","english":"and never","translit":"falan","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"نَّزِيدَكُمْ","english":"We will increase you","translit":"nazīdakum","root":"زيد"},{"position":4,"arabic":"إِلَّا","english":"except","translit":"illā","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"عَذَابًا","english":"(in) punishment","translit":"ʿadhāban","root":"عذب"}]},{"number":31,"translation":"Indeed, for the righteous is attainment -","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"إِنَّ","english":"Indeed","translit":"inna","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"لِلْمُتَّقِينَ","english":"for the righteous","translit":"lil'muttaqīna","root":"وقي"},{"position":3,"arabic":"مَفَازًا","english":"(is) success","translit":"mafāzan","root":"فوز"}]},{"number":32,"translation":"Gardens and grapevines","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"حَدَآئِقَ","english":"Gardens","translit":"ḥadāiqa","root":"حدق"},{"position":2,"arabic":"وَأَعْنَـٰبًۭا","english":"and grapevines","translit":"wa-aʿnāban","root":"عنب"}]},{"number":33,"translation":"And full-breasted [companions] of equal age","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَكَوَاعِبَ","english":"And splendid companions","translit":"wakawāʿiba","root":"كعب"},{"position":2,"arabic":"أَتْرَابًۭا","english":"well-matched","translit":"atrāban","root":"ترب"}]},{"number":34,"translation":"And a full cup.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَكَأْسًۭا","english":"And a cup","translit":"wakasan","root":"كأس"},{"position":2,"arabic":"دِهَاقًۭا","english":"full","translit":"dihāqan","root":"دهق"}]},{"number":35,"translation":"No ill speech will they hear therein or any falsehood -","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"لَّا","english":"Not","translit":"lā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"يَسْمَعُونَ","english":"they will hear","translit":"yasmaʿūna","root":"سمع"},{"position":3,"arabic":"فِيهَا","english":"therein","translit":"fīhā","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"لَغْوًۭا","english":"any vain talk","translit":"laghwan","root":"لغو"},{"position":5,"arabic":"وَلَا","english":"and not","translit":"walā","root":""},{"position":6,"arabic":"كِذَّٰبًۭا","english":"any falsehood","translit":"kidhāban","root":"كذب"}]},{"number":36,"translation":"[As] reward from your Lord, [a generous] gift [made due by] account,","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"جَزَآءًۭ","english":"(As) a reward","translit":"jazāan","root":"جزي"},{"position":2,"arabic":"مِّن","english":"from","translit":"min","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"رَّبِّكَ","english":"your Lord","translit":"rabbika","root":"ربب"},{"position":4,"arabic":"عَطَآءً","english":"a gift","translit":"ʿaṭāan","root":"عطو"},{"position":5,"arabic":"حِسَابًۭا","english":"(according to) account","translit":"ḥisāban","root":"حسب"}]},{"number":37,"translation":"[From] the Lord of the heavens and the earth and whatever is between them, the Most Merciful. They possess not from Him [authority for] speech.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"رَّبِّ","english":"Lord","translit":"rabbi","root":"ربب"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلسَّمَـٰوَٰتِ","english":"(of) the heavens","translit":"l-samāwāti","root":"سمو"},{"position":3,"arabic":"وَٱلْأَرْضِ","english":"and the earth","translit":"wal-arḍi","root":"أرض"},{"position":4,"arabic":"وَمَا","english":"and whatever","translit":"wamā","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"بَيْنَهُمَا","english":"(is) between both of them","translit":"baynahumā","root":"بين"},{"position":6,"arabic":"ٱلرَّحْمَـٰنِ ۖ","english":"the Most Gracious","translit":"l-raḥmāni","root":"رحم"},{"position":7,"arabic":"لَا","english":"not","translit":"lā","root":"","audio":"wbw/078_037_008.mp3"},{"position":8,"arabic":"يَمْلِكُونَ","english":"they have power","translit":"yamlikūna","root":"ملك","audio":"wbw/078_037_009.mp3"},{"position":9,"arabic":"مِنْهُ","english":"from Him","translit":"min'hu","root":"","audio":"wbw/078_037_010.mp3"},{"position":10,"arabic":"خِطَابًۭا","english":"(to) address","translit":"khiṭāban","root":"خطب","audio":"wbw/078_037_011.mp3"}]},{"number":38,"translation":"The Day that the Spirit and the angels will stand in rows, they will not speak except for one whom the Most Merciful permits, and he will say what is correct.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"يَوْمَ","english":"(The) Day","translit":"yawma","root":"يوم"},{"position":2,"arabic":"يَقُومُ","english":"will stand","translit":"yaqūmu","root":"قوم"},{"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلرُّوحُ","english":"the Spirit","translit":"l-rūḥu","root":"روح"},{"position":4,"arabic":"وَٱلْمَلَـٰٓئِكَةُ","english":"and the Angels","translit":"wal-malāikatu","root":"ملك"},{"position":5,"arabic":"صَفًّۭا ۖ","english":"(in) rows","translit":"ṣaffan","root":"صفف"},{"position":6,"arabic":"لَّا","english":"not","translit":"lā","root":"","audio":"wbw/078_038_007.mp3"},{"position":7,"arabic":"يَتَكَلَّمُونَ","english":"they will speak","translit":"yatakallamūna","root":"كلم","audio":"wbw/078_038_008.mp3"},{"position":8,"arabic":"إِلَّا","english":"except","translit":"illā","root":"","audio":"wbw/078_038_009.mp3"},{"position":9,"arabic":"مَنْ","english":"(one) who","translit":"man","root":"","audio":"wbw/078_038_010.mp3"},{"position":10,"arabic":"أَذِنَ","english":"permits","translit":"adhina","root":"أذن","audio":"wbw/078_038_011.mp3"},{"position":11,"arabic":"لَهُ","english":"[for] him","translit":"lahu","root":"","audio":"wbw/078_038_012.mp3"},{"position":12,"arabic":"ٱلرَّحْمَـٰنُ","english":"the Most Gracious","translit":"l-raḥmānu","root":"رحم","audio":"wbw/078_038_013.mp3"},{"position":13,"arabic":"وَقَالَ","english":"and he (will) say","translit":"waqāla","root":"قول","audio":"wbw/078_038_014.mp3"},{"position":14,"arabic":"صَوَابًۭا","english":"(what is) correct","translit":"ṣawāban","root":"صوب","audio":"wbw/078_038_015.mp3"}]},{"number":39,"translation":"That is the True Day; so he who wills may take to his Lord a [way of] return.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"ذَٰلِكَ","english":"That","translit":"dhālika","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلْيَوْمُ","english":"(is) the Day","translit":"l-yawmu","root":"يوم"},{"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلْحَقُّ ۖ","english":"the True","translit":"l-ḥaqu","root":"حقق"},{"position":4,"arabic":"فَمَن","english":"So whoever","translit":"faman","root":"","audio":"wbw/078_039_005.mp3"},{"position":5,"arabic":"شَآءَ","english":"wills","translit":"shāa","root":"شيأ","audio":"wbw/078_039_006.mp3"},{"position":6,"arabic":"ٱتَّخَذَ","english":"let him take","translit":"ittakhadha","root":"أخذ","audio":"wbw/078_039_007.mp3"},{"position":7,"arabic":"إِلَىٰ","english":"towards","translit":"ilā","root":"","audio":"wbw/078_039_008.mp3"},{"position":8,"arabic":"رَبِّهِۦ","english":"his Lord","translit":"rabbihi","root":"ربب","audio":"wbw/078_039_009.mp3"},{"position":9,"arabic":"مَـَٔابًا","english":"a return","translit":"maāban","root":"أوب","audio":"wbw/078_039_010.mp3"}]},{"number":40,"translation":"Indeed, We have warned you of a near punishment on the Day when a man will observe what his hands have put forth and the disbeliever will say, \"Oh, I wish that I were dust!\"","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"إِنَّآ","english":"Indeed We","translit":"innā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"أَنذَرْنَـٰكُمْ","english":"[We] have warned you","translit":"andharnākum","root":"نذر"},{"position":3,"arabic":"عَذَابًۭا","english":"(of) a punishment","translit":"ʿadhāban","root":"عذب"},{"position":4,"arabic":"قَرِيبًۭا","english":"near","translit":"qarīban","root":"قرب"},{"position":5,"arabic":"يَوْمَ","english":"(the) Day","translit":"yawma","root":"يوم"},{"position":6,"arabic":"يَنظُرُ","english":"will see","translit":"yanẓuru","root":"نظر"},{"position":7,"arabic":"ٱلْمَرْءُ","english":"the man","translit":"l-maru","root":"مرأ"},{"position":8,"arabic":"مَا","english":"what","translit":"mā","root":""},{"position":9,"arabic":"قَدَّمَتْ","english":"have sent forth","translit":"qaddamat","root":"قدم"},{"position":10,"arabic":"يَدَاهُ","english":"his hands","translit":"yadāhu","root":"يدي"},{"position":11,"arabic":"وَيَقُولُ","english":"and will say","translit":"wayaqūlu","root":"قول"},{"position":12,"arabic":"ٱلْكَافِرُ","english":"the disbeliever","translit":"l-kāfiru","root":"كفر"},{"position":13,"arabic":"يَـٰلَيْتَنِى","english":"O I wish","translit":"yālaytanī","root":""},{"position":14,"arabic":"كُنتُ","english":"I were","translit":"kuntu","root":"كون"},{"position":15,"arabic":"تُرَٰبًۢا","english":"dust","translit":"turāban","root":"ترب"}]}]}
